trans-unit.source: Provides the base authentication interface for Web client authentication modules.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder grunnleggende godkjenning-grensesnitt for Web-klienten godkjenningsmoduler.

trans-unit.source: The IAuthenticationModule interface defines the properties and methods that custom authentication modules must use.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IAuthenticationModule definerer egenskaper og metoder som egendefinert godkjenningsmoduler må bruke.

trans-unit.source: Authentication modules conduct the entire authentication process with a server, responding to an authentication challenge as appropriate.
trans-unit.target: Godkjenningsmoduler utføre hele godkjenning med en server, svarer på en godkjenningsforespørsel etter behov.

trans-unit.source: This process may consist of requests to an authentication server separate from the resource server, as well as any other activities required to properly authenticate a request for a URI.
trans-unit.target: Denne prosessen kan bestå av forespørsler til en egen fra ressursserveren, i tillegg til andre aktiviteter kreves for å godkjenne en forespørsel om riktig for en URI godkjenningsserveren.

trans-unit.source: Custom authentication modules should implement the IAuthenticationModule interface and then register with the <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Register%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: Egendefinert godkjenningsmoduler må implementere grensesnittet IAuthenticationModule og deretter Registrer den <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Register%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Register%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Authentication modules are also registered at program initialization by reading the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Godkjenningsmoduler er også registrert hos programinitialisering ved å lese konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: Returns an instance of the <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"></xref> class in respose to an authentication challenge from a server.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"> </xref> klassen i respose til en godkjenningsforespørsel fra en server.

trans-unit.source: The Authenticate method conducts the authentication process with the server and returns an <xref:System.Net.Authorization> instance to the <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager>.
trans-unit.target: Metoden Godkjenn utfører godkjenningsprosessen til serveren, og returnerer en <xref:System.Net.Authorization>forekomst til <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager>.</xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager> </xref:System.Net.Authorization>

trans-unit.source: The authentication challenge sent by the server.
trans-unit.target: Godkjenningsforespørsel som er sendt av serveren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> instance associated with the challenge.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>forekomst tilknyttet på forespørselen.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The credentials associated with the challenge.
trans-unit.target: Legitimasjonen som er forbundet med på forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"></xref> instance containing the authorization message for the request, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if the challenge cannot be handled.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"> </xref> inneholder authorization-melding for forespørselen, eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> Hvis på forespørselen ikke kan behandles.

trans-unit.source: Gets the authentication type provided by this authentication module.
trans-unit.target: Henter godkjenningstype fra denne modulen for godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: The AuthenticationType property identifies the authentication type implemented by this authentication module.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen AuthenticationType identifiserer godkjenningstype implementeres av denne modulen for godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: The AuthenticationType property is used by the <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Register%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to determine if the authentication module has been registered, and by the <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Unregister%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to remove a registered authentication module.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen AuthenticationType brukes av den <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Register%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode for å finne ut om godkjenning-modulen er registrert på, og den <xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Unregister%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metode for å fjerne en registrert godkjenningsmodul.</xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Unregister%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Net.AuthenticationManager.Register%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A string indicating the authentication type provided by this authentication module.
trans-unit.target: En tekststreng som angir godkjenning fra denne modulen for godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the authentication module supports preauthentication.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om modulen godkjenning støtter forhåndsgodkjenning.

trans-unit.source: The CanPreAuthenticate property is set to `true` to indicate that the authentication module can respond with a valid <xref:System.Net.Authorization> instance when the <xref:System.Net.IAuthenticationModule.PreAuthenticate%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CanPreAuthenticate er satt til `true` til å angi at modulen godkjenning kan svare med en gyldig <xref:System.Net.Authorization>serverforekomsten når den <xref:System.Net.IAuthenticationModule.PreAuthenticate%2A>-metoden.</xref:System.Net.IAuthenticationModule.PreAuthenticate%2A> </xref:System.Net.Authorization>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the authorization module supports preauthentication; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis modulen godkjenning støtter forhåndsgodkjenning; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns an instance of the <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"></xref> class for an authentication request to a server.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"> </xref> klasse for en forespørsel om godkjenning til en server.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Net.IAuthenticationModule.CanPreAuthenticate%2A> property is `true`, the PreAuthenticate method will return an instance of the <xref:System.Net.Authorization> class containing an authentication message.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.Net.IAuthenticationModule.CanPreAuthenticate%2A>egenskapen `true`, metoden PreAuthenticate tilbakestiller en forekomst av den <xref:System.Net.Authorization>klassen som inneholder en godkjenningsmelding.</xref:System.Net.Authorization> </xref:System.Net.IAuthenticationModule.CanPreAuthenticate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> instance associated with the authentication request.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>forekomst tilknyttet godkjenningsforespørselen.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The credentials associated with the authentication request.
trans-unit.target: Legitimasjonen som er forbundet med godkjenningsforespørselen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"></xref> instance containing the authorization message for the request.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Net.Authorization"> </xref> inneholder authorization-melding for forespørselen.
